1.title: Premiere
1.plot: In the series premiere, the gals chat about becoming promiscuous after 30, Sarah interrupts first dates, and Part 1 of an interview with Jeff Timmons from 98 Degrees

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: The Secrets Truth or Dare reveals, girls answers to guys dumb questions, date interrupted & part II of Jeff Timmons Interview

imdb.plot outline: Fresh off her nationally syndicated morning radio show to peruse a career in television, Sarah Fraser hosts a new and unique, interactive web series/talk show called "Hey Frase!" The program, features Sarah and a panel of sassy and overly opinionated women, who will fix the world, one man at a time. The women on the show have a wide variety of backgrounds and personalities. From the video gamer and the outspoken, to the mom, the beauty queen and the promiscuous. We would say that the show will be edgy, but that would be an understatement. Hey Frase will go the extremes to glorify, mock as well as create an open discussion on female (as well as male) perspectives on a variety of topics, such as: sex, dating, relationships, men, bizarre issues/problems, news topics as well as what the heck men are thinking and more.
